{"id": "ery8n2", "title": "Read This If You Have Weak Hands", "selftext": "THESE are the times that try men's hands. The summer autist and the sunshine bagholder will, in this crisis, shrink from the holding of their positions; but he that stands by it now, deserves the love and thanks of man and woman. Weak hands, like hell, is not easily conquered; yet we have this consolation with us, that the harder the conflict, the more glorious the gains. What we obtain too cheap, we esteem too lightly: it is dearness only that gives every thing its value. The market knows how to put a proper price upon its stonks; and it would be strange indeed if so celestial an article as TENDIES should not be highly rated.", "created_utc": 1579629023, "permalink": "/r/wallstreetbets/comments/ery8n2/read_this_if_you_have_weak_hands/", "is_self": true}